text: Ms. Marvel is an American TV miniseries that is part of the Marvel Cinematic Universe (MCU). Based on the Marvel Comics character Kamala Khan / Ms. Marvel, the series was created by Bisha K. Ali and was on Disney+ from June 8 to July 13, 2022. It is the seventh MCU TV series to be produced by Marvel Studios. It stars Iman Vellani as Kamala Khan.
